text: Sunaina Sunaina (20 April 1980) is an Indian weightlifter. Sunaina won three bronze medals at the 2002 Commonwealth Games in the 58 kg snatch, 58 kg clean and jerk and 58 kg total events. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Indian female weightlifters Category:Weightlifters at the 2002 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games bronze medallists for India Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in weightlifting
